The evidence with the title 'Sen. Brown: 'Hitler didn't want unions' ' says Mar 4, 2011  ... Sherrod Brown of Ohio invoked Adolf Hitler and Joseph Stalin while sounding off  ... “ i look back in history, in some of the worst governments that we had, you  ... Go after unions , Hitler did n't want unions, Stalin didn't want unions, Mubarak didn't want unions , these autocrats don't want independent unions, ” ... 
